		<title>Don&#8217;t Worry, The Federal Reserve Just Wants To Be Your &#8220;Online Friend&#8221;</title>
		<link>http://endoftheamericandream.com/archives/dont-worry-the-federal-reserve-just-wants-to-be-your-online-friend?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=dont-worry-the-federal-reserve-just-wants-to-be-your-online-friend</link>
		<comments>http://endoftheamericandream.com/archives/dont-worry-the-federal-reserve-just-wants-to-be-your-online-friend#comments</comments>
		<pubDate>Wed, 28 Sep 2011 21:57:04 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator>Michael</dc:creator>
				<category><![CDATA[Federal Reserve]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[Barack Obama]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[Bloggers]]></category>
