		<title>18 Examples Of How Christians Are Being Specifically Targeted By Big Brother</title>
		<link>http://endoftheamericandream.com/archives/18-examples-of-how-christians-are-being-specifically-targeted-by-big-brother?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=18-examples-of-how-christians-are-being-specifically-targeted-by-big-brother</link>
