		<title>New World Trade Center Tower To Be Made With Glass From China And Steel From Germany</title>
		<link>http://endoftheamericandream.com/archives/new-world-trade-center-tower-to-be-made-with-glass-from-china-and-steel-from-germany?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=new-world-trade-center-tower-to-be-made-with-glass-from-china-and-steel-from-germany</link>
		<comments>http://endoftheamericandream.com/archives/new-world-trade-center-tower-to-be-made-with-glass-from-china-and-steel-from-germany#comments</comments>
		<pubDate>Thu, 22 Sep 2011 21:52:15 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator>Michael</dc:creator>
